io albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Title\n!colspan=\"7\"| Peak chart positions\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Certifications\n|-\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=\"UK\">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/614/marillion/|title=MARILLION {{!}} full Official Chart history|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=2016-10-14}}</ref><ref name=\"Zobbel\">[http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK_M.HTM Chart Log UK: M] Zobbel.de</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[GfK Entertainment Charts|GER]]<br><ref name=\"German Album Charting\">{{cite web|url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/suche?artistId=Marillion|title=Discographie von Marillion|publisher=GfK Entertainment|accessdate=4 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[Netherlands|NLD]]<br><ref name=\"NLD\">{{cite web |url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Marillion |title=dutchcharts.nl - Discografie Marillion |publisher=dutchcharts.nl |accessdate=2010-01-05 }}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[Norway|NOR]]<br><ref name=\"NOR\">{{cite web |url=http://lista.vg.no/artist/marillion/3281 |title=VG-lista - Chart position in Norway |publisher=www.vg.no |accessdate=2013-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170413072518/http://lista.vg.no/artist/marillion/3281 |archive-date=13 April 2017 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[Sweden|SWE]]<br><ref name=\"SWE\">{{cite web |url=http://swedishcharts.com/search.asp?search=marillion&cat=a |title=swedishcharts.com - Swedish Charts Portal |publisher=swedishcharts.com |accessdate=2010-01-05 }}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[Switzerland|SWI]]<br><ref name=\"SWI\">{{cite web |url=http://hitparade.ch/search.asp?search=Marillion&cat=a |title=Die Offizielle Schweizer Hitparade und Music Community |publisher=hitparade.ch |accessdate=2010-01-05 }}</ref>\n\n!style=\"width:4em;font-size:75%\"|[[Billboard 200