able\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Title\n!width=\"45\"|<small>[[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=\"UK\"/></small>\n!width=\"45\"|<small>[[Netherlands|NLD]]<br><ref name=\"NLD\"/></small>\n!width=\"45\"|<small>[[Switzerland|SWI]]<br><ref name=\"SWI\"/></small>\n!width=\"45\"|<small>[[Billboard 200|US]]<br><ref name=\"everyhit.com\"/></small>\n!BPI certification\n!Notes\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[The Singles '82\u201388'|The Singles '82\u2013'88]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| Re-released as three-disc box in 2009\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''Singles Box Volume 2 '89\u2013'95''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| Re-released as four-disc box in 2013\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Early Stages|Early Stages \u2013 The Official Bootleg Box Set]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''The Official Bootleg Box Set Volume 2''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\u2014\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Year\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Title\n!colspan=\"7\"|Peak chart positions\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Album\n|-\n!width=\"30\"|<small>[[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=\"UK\"/><ref name=\"Zobbel\"/></small>\n!width=\"30\"|<small>[[Germany|GER]]<br><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/MARILLION/single |title=German Singles Charting |access-date=8 F